        <updateDate>2019-11-19T20:23:08Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>School Safety Clearinghouse Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) to establish a School Safety Clearinghouse as a central resource for&nbsp;evidence-based practices and other information on school-safety topics.</p> <p>DHS shall develop tiers for determining evidence-based practices that demonstrate a significant effect on improving the health, safety, and welfare of persons in school settings.</p> ]]></text>
      </summary>
